uper Sonico</span><h3 class=\"text-lg md:text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter group-hover/info:text-blue-400 transition-colors uppercase italic leading-tight line-clamp-2\">Super Sonico - Bicute Bunnies (Blue ver)</h3><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-3 border-t border-gray-900 pt-3\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\">Value</span><span class=\"text-base font-black text-white italic\">RM <!-- -->98.00</span></div></a></div></div></section><section id=\"ethos\" class=\"bg-transparent py-32 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[15vw] md:text-[20vw] font-black text-white/5 whitespace-nowrap italic tracking-tighter pointer-events-none select-none\">THE ETHOS</div><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-24 relative z-10 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-blue-600 mb-2\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">100% Verified</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[250px]\">No bootlegs. No recasts. Every item is verified against manufacturer records before entering our catalog.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock text-white mb-2\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">Secure Transport</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[250px]\">Figures are packed in impact-resistant casing before dispatch. While we cannot control external couriers, we remain reachable if an item is damaged in transit.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu text-blue-600 mb-2\"><rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" x=\"4\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"6\" height=\"6\" x=\"9\" y=\"9\" rx=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M15 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M15 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 20v2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">Order Tracking</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[250px]\">Your order history is digitized. Track your purchases and collection seamlessly within your dashboard.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"syndicate\" class=\"bg-[#111] max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 text-center rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-800 relative group overflow-hidden mt-16\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000 z-0 pointer-events-none mix-blend-screen\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter mb-6 relative inline-block\">JOIN THE SYNDICATE.<span class=\"absolute -top-6 -right-10 text-[10px] bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-black uppercase tracking-widest not-italic\">Secured</span></h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base mb-12 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed\">The highest-tier drops go fast. Submit your email to get early access to new drops before they go public.</p><form class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Enter your email address...\" class=\"flex-grow bg-[#050505] border border-gray-700 text-white px-8 py-5 text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase font-black tracking-widest focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-600 transition-all placeholder:text-gray-700\" required=\"\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white px-10 py-5 font-black text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all whitespace-nowrap shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(37,99,235,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(255,255,255,0.5)]\">Request Access</button></form></div></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-gray-900 bg-[#020202] py-8 text-center relative z-10 w-full mt-auto\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a class=\"text-gray-800 hover:text-red-600 transition-colors duration-500\" title=\"Restricted Access\" href=\"/admin/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-network\"><rect x=\"16\" y=\"16\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect x=\"2\" y=\"16\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect x=\"9\" y=\"2\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" rx=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M5 16v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h12a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3\"></path><path d=\"M12 12V8\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"text-gray-600 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Vault 6 Studios